              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Ion source: Incident pions were generated as secondary",
                "beam. The TOF of incident particles was measured for",
                "separation of pi+ mesons from protons by the use of a",
                "pair of Pilot U scintillators."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "- Target is natural.",
                "- Chemical-form of target is element.",
                "- Physical-form of target is solid.",
                "- Target-thickness: 4.9cm in diameter and 3.0cm thick",
                "- Backing is unknown."
